name: Open Rentals
description: Count of open rentals since the start of the current year
originalSql: SELECT Count(*) AS value FROM CustomerFile WHERE CustomerStatus = 'Open' AND CreatedDate >= DateSerial(Year(Date()), 1, 1)
finalSql: SELECT Count(*) AS value FROM CustomerFile WHERE CustomerStatus = 'Open' AND CreatedDate >= DateSerial(Year(Date()), 1, 1)

name: New Rentals Jan
description: Count of new rentals for January of the current year
originalSql: SELECT Count(*) AS value FROM CustomerFile WHERE CustomerStatus = 'Open' AND Month(CreatedDate) = 1 AND Year(CreatedDate) = Year(Date())
finalSql: SELECT Count(*) AS value FROM CustomerFile WHERE CustomerStatus = 'Open' AND Month(CreatedDate) = 1 AND Year(CreatedDate) = Year(Date())
